     <div class="mod text-mod tabbed-content m-news text-mod"> 
      <div class="title">
       Registrar Updates
      </div> 
      <div class="panel"> 
       <div class="container"> 
        <div class="text"> 
         <p><a href="http://www.nyit.edu/register"><img src="http://www.nyit.edu/images/uploads/about/register.png" border="0" alt="register" style="float:left; padding: 0px 5px 0 0;"></a> </p>
         <h3>Academic Advisement and Registration Spring 2015</h3> 
         <p>- <a href="http://www.nyit.edu/register">Academic advisement &amp; registration</a><br> - <a href="https://nyitcs.nyit.edu/psp/ps/EMPLOYEE/HRMS/c/COMMUNITY_ACCESS.CLASS_SEARCH.GBL">Search for classes</a><br> - <a href="http://www.nyit.edu/files/uploads/00/campus_life/FinAid-Reg.pdf">Financial aid &amp; registration</a> (PDF)<br></p> 
         <p>- <a href="http://www.nyit.edu/managing_your_classes/resources/resources_exams">Final exam schedules Fall 2014</a><br> - No classes scheduled Nov. 26 to Nov. 30. Administrative offices closed.<br> - Incomplete grades earned for Spring or Summer 2014 expire Dec. 20. Submit your missing coursework to the instructor before these deadlines to avoid changing an I to IF<br> - Apply for May 2015 graduation by Feb. 13, 2015. Students must apply online at NYITConnect.<br> <br> </p> 
         <p>- <a href="http://catalog.nyit.edu/">Catalogs 2014-2015</a><br> - <a href="/courses">Course descriptions</a></p>
         <p><br> </p> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="status"></div> 
     </div> 
     <br> 
    </div>
